i vote for making moonflair summoner's rift accessible. or! making a new version of it called sunflair with increased AP, decreased magic resist, increased armor, and a new unique passive called - Solarity = taking consecutive hits over time grants stacks of solarity. solarity stacks grant basic attacks a buff that applies sun burn to targets over 2 seconds. sun burn deals 3% more damage from magic based attacks and spells. *HOT HOT HOT* when killing a player at max stacks by sun burn their body will erupt in flames and burst putting the passive on cooldown for 90 seconds.

Skilled players could just dodge an ultimate, e.g. Veigar 2000 stack ult.

How about this: {{item:3191}} 
UNIQUE -- STASIS: After a 3 second delay, put yourself in stasis for 2.5 seconds, rendering yourself untargetable and invulnerable for the duration, but  also unable to move, attack, cast spells, or use items during this time. You are slowed by 20% during the delay, increasing to 100% by the end.
